old medal\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday, the pair created another touching moment during the men's high jump qualification round at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 230}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"another touching moment\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 272}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's high jump qualification round\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Barshim was preparing for his final jump of the qualification, the Qatar native pulled up with an apparent injury, hopping on one foot before falling to the ground in pain.The first person to check on Barshim?\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\", \"score\": 0.9999065801841078, \"rank\": 9.342812027063941e-05, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"his final jump\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualification\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"an apparent injury\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"one foot\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"The first person\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making the gesture even more sportsmanlike was the fact that Tamberi had failed his jump attempt just moments before.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gesture\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"his jump attempt\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Italian wasn't thinking about that.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9945184545886248, \"rank\": 0.005498328075914036, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi rushed up to Barshim and helped him to stretch out his leg as a medical team member from Puerto Rico also approached the Qatari high jumper to assist in aid.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9952570925003715, \"rank\": 0.004607250169135794, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"his leg\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"a medical team member\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"the Qatari high jumper\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"aid\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the treatment, Barshim was ultimately able to complete another jump at a height of 2.27 meters, good enough to advance the Qatari to Saturday's final.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the treatment\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"another jump\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"a height\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"2.27 meters\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the Qatari\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday's final\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi, who jumped at 2.24 meters, also qualified for the final just days after he was hospitalized with suspected kidney problems.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"2.24 meters\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"suspected kidney problems\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago, Tamberi and Barshim created one of the most heartwarming moments at the Tokyo Olympics after neither could outdo the other, leaving them tied at 2.37-meter jumps and prompting an official to call for a \\\"jump-off\\\" to determine who would take home gold.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"the most heartwarming moments\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"2.37-meter jumps\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"an official\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"jump-off\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"home gold\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These two \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b9#Olympicspic.twitter.com/sMLSyIGlbK But Barshim, in an honorable moment, asked the official, \\\"Can we have two golds?\\\"\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These two \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b9#Olympicspic.twitter.com/sMLSyIGlbK\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"But Barshim\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"an honorable moment\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"the official\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's possible, yes,\\\" the official replied.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the official\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"History my friend, Olympic champions,\\\" Barshim said as he clasped hands with Tamberi.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friend\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champions\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"hands\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi then leapt into Barshim's arms and shouted out in elation.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim's arms\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"elation\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's only fitting that the two would both come to symbolize the height of sportsmanship and friendship at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the height\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"friendship\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Load